{"tid":416195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BMW]中大學生會回應：涉事司機或成協助犯罪　斥學生「英國走狗」違道德","createTime":"2017-09-27T15:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T13:54:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"193e55ccfcfa11cd00f02a362c42097756e1d639","tid":416195,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506517155312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506517155312&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=fe32da34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506517155312&h=c13fadab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506517155312</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00001/a230e157d3ea7b95f628e3b2a343b345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2Fa230e157d3ea7b95f628e3b2a343b345.jpg&h=18c08b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學民主牆上早前出現「拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立」標語單張，一名女士在本月17日突然撕走標語，其後乘坐私家車離開。私家車後來駛回現場，司機開窗並大叫「英國走狗」。運輸署資料顯示，私家車車主與中大信息工程學系榮譽教授李碩彥同名。<br />\n<br />\n中文大學學生會今夜回應事件，認為報道中男司機的樣貌與李碩彥極為相似，加上運輸署的資料，「令人有合理懷疑該協助民主牆海報女子逃離現場的男司機就是李碩彥教授。」<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會指，如果該司機真的是中大教授，其行為「令人極度震驚」，故促請校方調查並追究校內刑事毀壞行為，並詢問校方處理手法。<br />\n<br />\n學生會指，該司機雖無直接破壞民主牆，但協助破壞民主牆海報的女子逃離現場，已有可能構成協助犯罪。學生會又指，該司機將「英國」與「走狗」相提並論的言論不尊重別國，有違道德規範及社會的期望，除傷害英國籍或其他與英國有關係的師生外，亦破壞學校國際聲譽。"},{"pid":"84c5c78dd20298269efeac1fbf6902e72d311cc8","tid":416195,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"我愛支那，但我開BMW<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8721be5ac491c70b9b391f93901f5693491a879","tid":416195,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d906aac6ff00460d7f8807226850b124597a70","tid":416195,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"做得岩!!"},{"pid":"b35143517e4610ef972979db057ab04bedeaa59a","tid":416195,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"超越道德既底線"},{"pid":"98ff779175c2581eaeeac51215a62a1738167e59","tid":416195,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506517155312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506517155312&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=fe32da34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506517155312&h=c13fadab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506517155312</a>"},{"pid":"dd05f621c49ef42582720c3d49afb2bdb6176e9f","tid":416195,"uid":76261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7808c8c2aa909a47d2eb3ede8cd7365039a5f6e4","tid":